      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 protocol followed at both laboratories; loading rate (5 mm/min) and fixture geometry verified. However, only a single test condition (compression-bending at standard F1717 geometry) was evaluated; no variation in offset distance or loading angle was explored. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3), representing a known gap accepted by the credibility assessment team with documented rationale."
