      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Eq. 4 for each QoI and each specimen. All values below 1.96. Percent differences: stiffness 4.2±2.1%, yield force 6.8±3.4%, force at 40 mm 5.1±2.7%. Pre-established acceptance bounds satisfied. Cross-laboratory reproducibility confirmed with inter-lab coefficient of variation <5%."
    },
